#Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [1.0.0] - 2019-01-22
- Modified create_purchase_order.php view file


## [1.0.0] - 2019-01-09
- Modified Requisitions Controller
- Modified Requisitions_Model
- Modified Products_Model
- Modified Reports Controller
- Added view to reports view folder
- Modified views in reports view folder
- Created table requisition_category_log
- Created table inventory_category_log
- Modified ProductScanner Controller

## [1.0.0] - 2018-12-27
- Created category_amount_history table to store the amount of items that were in a category at a given date
- Created app_updates table to be able to log and show updates to the application to the users. The table was created to show updates to a particular group of users also

## [1.0.0] - 2018-05-12
- Created daily_requisition_cost
- Created monthly_requisition_cost
- Modified Forms Controller
- Modified Requisitions model
- Modified Products model
- Modified create_requisition in forms view folder